title: Dana Kellin Moonstone Mix Gold Necklace
description:
A stone for new beginnings, Moonstone evokes inner growth and strength, soothing emotional disruption and eliciting calm and good fortune. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details and high quality materials.

  • Dimensions: overall length 16.9 in, large moonstones approx 0.375 x 0.5 in
  • Materials: 14/20 goldfill, moonstones, labradorite, crystals, seed beads
